Text: Hi @raymond_u - thank you for being so fast again. For those interested, there is an interview with Jenson Button, Alain Prost drives the Red Bull RB6 (from 2010) and there is a 28-page technology special on touring cars (including BTCC, DTM, Aussie V8s and Historics). Well worth a download!!
